      "message": "Yes. It\u0027s not in `master`. This migration is a migration for the SQL script as found in git revision 00597b5c8325664c2c534625525f59232d243d66 (see comment at the top). The idea behind this is having a dedicated migration for the changes introduced by every git revision. That way we can stamp the current in-database schema with the alembic revision for the git revision it was created from and proceed incrementally with regular migrations from that point onward.",
      "parentUuid": "9f6a8fd7_4435a1f6",
